_______________________________________________________________________________
"Guild Chat"
        This allows guild members to talk on the guild channel and is
        automatically added to the player's power list when joining the
        guild.  Note that it does NOT include the high level guild chat.
        Obviously, this power cannot be forgotten.
 
SP Cost:  none		Guild Level:  1		Potential Points:  0
 
Command:  psi <msg>, epsi <emote>, or psi :<in-game emote>
